## Synthesis Task

### Step 1: Identify Must-Fixes
Extract all must-fixes from all responses. A must-fix is **cross-cutting** if raised by ≥3 personas.

### Step 2: Revise the Journey
Revise the journey to address all cross-cutting must-fixes. For each changed step, annotate with the must-fix number(s) it addresses.

Respond ONLY with YAML:

```yaml
must_fixes:
  - number: 1
    description: "[clear, actionable description]"
    raised_by_persona_ids: ["UXW-01", "UXW-02"]
    is_cross_cutting: true  # true if ≥3 personas raised it

secondary_asks:
  - number: 10
    description: "[raised by 1-2 personas only]"
    raised_by_persona_ids: ["UXW-03"]
    is_cross_cutting: false

revised_journey_steps:
  - step_number: 1
    screen_or_route: "[route]"
    affordance: "[what the user can do here]"
    copy_sample: "[suggested copy]"
    principle_reference: "[design principle]"
    must_fix_numbers: [1, 3]  # which must-fixes this step addresses; empty if unchanged

average_score: {{ scores | sum / scores | length }}
```
